    "description": "PIA Corporation engages in the ticketing/publishing/planning, production, and operation of concerts and events in Japan. The company distributes tickets through online computer ticketing system for music, sports, theater, film, leisure events, etc., including internet, convenience stores, shops, telephone, and member services. It also publishes books and magazine books; and provides business solutions, including promotion and sales services, and planning customer management strategy services for entertainment promoters/sports associations/theater troupes, venues, theaters, stadiums, and TV stations/production, as well as concert and event organizers, such as co-sponsors, investors, etc. In addition, the company is involved in organizing, planning, producing, and managing various entertainment events, such as music festivals, stages, original events, films, and topical events; and develops contents for the leisure and entertainment fields through various platforms comprising web media/APP, portal site/SNS, and magazine/mook/publications. Further, the company manages live houses, halls, theatres, and arenas; and handles ticket sales management for various international conventions. PIA Corporation was founded in 1972 and is headquartered in Tokyo, Japan."
